36:12.300 --> 36:14.300
or even having an actual show

36:14.400 --> 36:16.800
so she'd see that I wasn't going to fail.

36:16.900 --> 36:19.400
He wanted to prove himself to you.

36:19.700 --> 36:20.900
He wanted to make a sale, and--

36:21.000 --> 36:23.800
that's why he got so angry
when I wouldn't help him.

36:24.500 --> 36:26.300
Yeah, I wasn't fair.

36:26.900 --> 36:28.100
To either of them.

36:28.200 --> 36:30.800
He knows that you were just trying to protect him.

36:31.200 --> 36:33.100
Tell her that I'm so sorry.

36:33.700 --> 36:35.200
I will.

36:35.800 --> 36:38.700
But I ended up hurting the one I loved the most.

36:38.800 --> 36:41.300
He feels terrible about what happened.

36:41.700 --> 36:45.500
He wanted the truth to come about
what he had done and how he had hurt you.

36:46.400 --> 36:49.100
And he knew you'd be the only that could tell it.

36:53.400 --> 36:57.000
I just wanted to mean
as much to you as your work did.

36:57.200 --> 37:00.100
And I loved the way you looked at the world.
I just...

37:01.000 --> 37:03.500
wondered, did you see me?

37:05.300 --> 37:08.000
Sophie, you were in everything that I did.

37:08.100 --> 37:10.900
And everything that I made,
you were a part of it all.

37:12.400 --> 37:14.300
Can you make her understand?

37:19.700 --> 37:21.600
Is that the light?

37:22.800 --> 37:25.200
It's so incredible.

37:27.200 --> 37:30.900
Look... you tell her that
I can't go unless I know she's forgiven me.

37:31.000 --> 37:33.300
He needs to know that you forgive him.

37:40.300 --> 37:42.400
I forgive you, kevin.

37:43.500 --> 37:47.200
And I'm not sorry that I loved you.
At least I know I can.

37:54.500 --> 37:56.300
He's gone.

38:21.900 --> 38:23.900
a picture = 1000 words
here's one - thanks

38:53.200 --> 38:54.900
I hate fighting.

38:55.800 --> 38:58.000
Neither of us ever wins.

38:59.100 --> 39:01.700
I know you're just trying to protect me.

39:02.000 --> 39:07.000
I've been thinking a lot about the
dark spirits don't just lurk underground.

39:07.500 --> 39:10.000
That they're around me all the time.

39:10.600 --> 39:13.500
I just want you to know
that that doesn't scare me.

39:13.700 --> 39:15.300
How is that reassuring?

39:15.400 --> 39:20.700
Because...anger and darkness, that's just

39:21.000 --> 39:24.400
the stuff we're supposed to
unravel and learn from.

39:25.500 --> 39:29.100
And I do that all the time, with the spirits.

39:32.400 --> 39:35.100
And I'm not afraid because...

39:37.400 --> 39:40.300
I know that love is stronger.

39:41.200 --> 39:43.200
I've seen it.

39:48.400 --> 39:51.400
Ok. No decisions based on fear.

39:51.500 --> 39:54.100
No decisions based on fear.

39:55.800 --> 39:57.900
Does that include trigonometry
and organic chemistry,

39:58.000 --> 39:59.400
because these are terrifying.

39:59.500 --> 40:02.200
It means a whole year of undergrad courses
before I can even apply.

40:02.300 --> 40:03.900
Oh, my god.

40:05.300 --> 40:06.900
You're gonna do it, aren't you?

40:07.000 --> 40:09.400
Well, if you can fight the forces of evil,
I think I can do pre-med.

40:09.500 --> 40:10.800
Say it.

40:11.200 --> 40:13.100
I really need to hear you say it.

40:13.200 --> 40:15.300
I want to be a doctor.

40:18.100 --> 40:19.000
What are you getting?

40:19.100 --> 40:23.200
Just...close your eyes.
I got you something.

40:28.400 --> 40:29.500
Ok.

40:30.500 --> 40:35.100
Pick a city or a town,
doesn't matter how big or how small.

40:35.700 --> 40:38.000
When you get into med school,

40:38.500 --> 40:41.000
I'll be right there with you.

